Availability:Public
Title: Basic Controls
Crumbs: %ROOT%, Engine, Engine/UI, Engine/UI/LevelEditor, Engine/UI/LevelEditor/Details
Description:Simple property types such as numeric boxes and spinners, text boxes, checkboxes, radio buttons, and comboboxes.
Version: 4.9

Unreal Editor has many simple control types you are familiar with for editing numeric values, text, etc.

| Control | Description |
| ------- | ----------- |
| **Text Box** | Used for text properties, such as `FString` and `FName`. [INCLUDE:#TypeString] |
| **Numeric Box** | Can be used for editing any numeric property, such as `Integers` and `Floats`. [INCLUDE:#TypeNumericBox] |
| **Numeric Spinner** | Can be used for editing any numeric property, such as `Integers` and `Floats`. [INCLUDE:#TypeNumericSpinner] |
| **Checkbox** | Used for editing simple toggle properties such as `Bools`. [INCLUDE:#TypeBool] |
| **Dropdown** | Used for editing `Enums` and other properties that provide a list of available values. [INCLUDE:#TypeEnum] |

